**`recalculateDots(markers:valuesOption:)`** — замена старого `recalculateDots()`. Статическое вычисление в фоне, результат применяется на главном акторе:

```swift
private func recalculateDots(markers: Set<TrackMarker>, valuesOption: TrackScreenOptions.Values) async {
    guard !Task.isCancelled else { return }
    let result = Self.computeDotsResult(markers: markers, valuesOption: valuesOption)
    await MainActor.run { [self] in
        guard !Task.isCancelled else { return }
        maxMarkerValue = result.maxValue
        minMarkerValue = result.minValue
        mapValues = result.mapValues
    }
    await updateCurrentDots()
}

private struct DotsResult {
    let mapValues: [Int: Int]
    let maxValue: Float?
    let minValue: Float?
}

private static func computeDotsResult(
    markers: Set<TrackMarker>,
    valuesOption: TrackScreenOptions.Values
) -> DotsResult {
    let filteredValues = markers.nonEmptyValues(type: valuesOption)
    guard let maxValue = filteredValues.max(), let minValue = filteredValues.min(), minValue != maxValue else {
        let mapValues = markers.reduce(into: [Int: Int]()) {
            $0[$1.timestamp] = $1.isEmpty ? -1 : GMSTrackMarkerConsts.maxColorValue
        }
        return DotsResult(mapValues: mapValues, maxValue: nil, minValue: nil)
    }
    let mapValues = computeMapValues(markers: markers, valuesOption: valuesOption, maxValue: maxValue, minValue: minValue)
    return DotsResult(mapValues: mapValues, maxValue: maxValue, minValue: minValue)
}

private static func computeMapValues(
    markers: Set<TrackMarker>,
    valuesOption: TrackScreenOptions.Values,
    maxValue: Float,
    minValue: Float
) -> [Int: Int] {
    let valueRange = maxValue - minValue
    let maxDefaultValue = Float(GMSTrackMarkerConsts.maxColorValue)
    return markers.reduce(into: [Int: Int]()) { result, marker in
        let value: Int
        if marker.isEmpty {
            value = -1
        } else {
            let markerValue = valuesOption == .dose ? marker.doseRate : marker.countRate
            let colorValue = maxDefaultValue - (markerValue - minValue) / valueRange * maxDefaultValue
            value = Int(colorValue)
        }
        result[marker.timestamp] = value
    }
}
```

